Waifur inflation
As waifurs™ are mined from 4chan from a time t0 to a time t1 the marginal value of the next waifur found goes to zero, this is called waifur inflation. For instance, if you were to flood the /hmofa/ market with 50 rare sarahs, the overall price of sarahs will drop. The overall inflation is a function of the amount of sarahs that were pumped and the time interval of the pumping.
